        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> There seems to be one from Kevin, https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/logging-analytics/+/102099\n> \n> Kevin can you confirm if the fix is expected to be included in Frankfurt release ?\n\nI'll just update the version.  This needs to move forward.",
